<section id="转折点在-2011-年中期" class="level3">
<h3><a href="#转折点在-2011-年中期" title="Link to section: § &#39;转折点在 201115ya 年中期&#39;">转折点在 <span class="date-range">2011<sub><span title="2011 was 15 years ago.">15ya</span></sub></span> 年中期</a></h3>
<p>将 <span class="date-range">2012<sub><span title="2012 was 14 years ago.">14ya</span></sub></span> 年之前视为不同时期的新模型具有更好的拟合度。我们能做得更好吗？<a href="http://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/changepoint/index.html" id="_1THWRQu0" data-link-icon="R" data-link-icon-type="text" data-link-icon-color="#1b61b1"><code>changepoint</code></a><span> 包将 <span class="date-range">2011<sub><span title="2011 was 15 years ago.">15ya</span></sub></span> 年 5 月/6 月指认为罪魁祸首，并给出了更大的均值差异（254 对 147）：</span></p>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb13"><pre class="sourceCode R"><code class="sourceCode r"><span id="cb13-1"><a href="#cb13-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="fu">library</span>(changepoint)</span>
<span id="cb13-2"><a href="#cb13-2" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="fu">plot</span>(<span class="fu">cpt.meanvar</span>(alertsRecent<span class="sc">$</span>Links), <span class="at">ylab=</span><span class="st">&quot;Links&quot;</span>)</span></code></pre></div>
<figure>
<p><img alt="2010–201313ya 年的链接数，显示 201115ya 年 5 月/6 月的体制转变" data-aspect-ratio="1 / 1" decoding="async" height="100" id="_xCD7o1a-" loading="lazy" src="/images/google/alerts/changepoint.png" width="100"></img></p>
<figcaption><p><span class="date-range" title="The date range 2010–2013 lasted 3 years, ending 13 years ago.">2010–2013<sub><span title="2010 was 16 years ago.">13ya</span></sub></span> 年的链接数，显示 <span class="date-range">2011<sub><span title="2011 was 15 years ago.">15ya</span></sub></span> 年 5 月/6 月的体制转变</p></figcaption>
</figure>
